    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine has a noticeable knock and struggles with cold starts, while the transmission shifts roughly between gears. The body shows extensive rust, several large dents, and the paint is peeling in multiple areas. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and some electronics are non-functional. This car is being sold as-is and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts.",
