    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a project with potential? This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, making it a budget-friendly choice for a mechanic or DIY enthusiast ready to bring it back to life! While it needs significant TLC and mechanical attention, it's a great opportunity to own a car with character at a fraction of the cost. Perfect for those who love a rewarding challenge!",
